{"tid":912860,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[全港最平] 瑞和街 橙售價為12元3個、菜心每斤9元，而生菜為5元一斤","createTime":"2018-11-23T03:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T07:31:44.000Z","uid":54373,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7387e333ed665914135497f14795c4cc8c979e69","tid":912860,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:48:11.000Z","msg":"報告顯示，北區及觀塘區較香港其他地區的貧窮情況嚴重，當區的物價因而較其他地區低。觀塘區區議員鄭景陽表示，觀塘區內街市較將軍澳區便宜一至兩成。他今日到觀塘瑞和街街市，以及將軍澳寶林街市進行實地考察和比較，<span style=\"color: red;\">發現瑞和街街市的香橙售價為12元3個、菜心每斤9元，而生菜為5元一斤</span>；寶林街市方面，香橙售價為18元3個、菜心每斤12元，生菜則為7元一斤，可見觀塘街市物價明顯較將軍澳街市「平民」，鄭景陽更表示見過有觀塘區的長者趁街市臨收檔時段，才專程到場買減價尾貨。<br />\n<br />\n鄭景陽解釋，由於當區社區基層人口多，菜檔會調整自身市場定位，若賣得太貴會失去競爭優勢，另外近年觀塘多了直銷菜檔，直接由內地取貨來港，並以優惠價錢賣給街坊，因此當區街市的物價都較便宜。"},{"pid":"c2908b1c045cfa5064ee4720848b95dc6873524a","tid":912860,"uid":4574,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:50:19.000Z","msg":"內地直銷菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11bfe0351f44da0213397809ae32a3c4916fa9e3","tid":912860,"uid":179967,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:52:47.000Z","msg":"寧願平仲好<br />\n貴既都好得去邊<br />\n前幾日買橙40蚊6個又話甜又話多汁又成<br />\n剝出黎全部都係乾到仆街得渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n菜又係苦到仆街"},{"pid":"567f571f700f371d93fcd7c156abd67f158ccedd","tid":912860,"uid":442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:54:56.000Z","msg":"上次係觀塘買餸<br />\n街市外個d 舖買條菜心都要行幾間舖<br />\n反而街市內個d 一間搞掂<br />\n其實出面d 舖係咪合謀經營<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6df77f4161d49e666109294ac0e38294af26ac5","tid":912860,"uid":166766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"567f571f700f371d93fcd7c156abd67f158ccedd","tid":912860,"uid":442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:54:56.000Z","msg":"上次係觀塘買餸<br />\n街市外個d 舖買條菜心都要行幾間舖<br />\n反而街市內個d 一間搞掂<br />\n其實出面d 舖係咪合謀經營<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:01:50.000Z","msg":"好多菜檔老闆都係同一個人  而且黑底<br />\n賣菜已經好少檔仔賣<br />\n街市二樓有檔賣菜個老細無啦啦響自己個朵凶個客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n&quot;我係xxx&quot;"},{"pid":"472ef576069006a14ee4e6d075de03c5f69fafe2","tid":912860,"uid":20337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:05:04.000Z","msg":"個啲菜落硫酸銅落到爆<br />\n菜心條框入面白心 層皮起渣嘅<br />\n生菜係唔爽脆 未發育好一㩒就碎哂個種嘛<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/wOyaQE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FwOyaQE.gif&h=1aabc20c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5286e96b7bdae6c1856df81468793f34af1a66b","tid":912860,"uid":22291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"472ef576069006a14ee4e6d075de03c5f69fafe2","tid":912860,"uid":20337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:05:04.000Z","msg":"個啲菜落硫酸銅落到爆<br />\n菜心條框入面白心 層皮起渣嘅<br />\n生菜係唔爽脆 未發育好一㩒就碎哂個種嘛<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/wOyaQE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FwOyaQE.gif&h=1aabc20c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:10:44.000Z","msg":"唔知就自己落去行下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d339c615eba933128dbcb35beb93031b9194f14","tid":912860,"uid":372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5286e96b7bdae6c1856df81468793f34af1a66b","tid":912860,"uid":22291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"472ef576069006a14ee4e6d075de03c5f69fafe2","tid":912860,"uid":20337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:05:04.000Z","msg":"個啲菜落硫酸銅落到爆<br />\n菜心條框入面白心 層皮起渣嘅<br />\n生菜係唔爽脆 未發育好一㩒就碎哂個種嘛<br />\n<img src=\"https